Isabel West https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isabel_West 0 Isabel West, also known as Isabelle West (1858 – July 22, 1942) was an American film actress in the late 1910s and early 1920s. She began her career in 1916 as Mrs. Harris in The Blue Envelope Mystery.She died in Brentwood, Long Island, New York, US.
